<div id = "instructions">
    <h4>Instructions:</h4>
    <p>The letters of the English alphabet are jumbled and you have to put them in the right order.<br>
        To do that, you have to drag a specific letter and drop it in a square.<br>
        You have 1 minute(however, it is set to 5 seconds so that it can be tested<br> without waiting much time)
        to put the letters in the right order.<br>
        Click on 'Start' button to initiate the timer.
    </p>
</div>

